title: BDE-SYSTEMS Corvette C4, Lowering 10" Bolt Kit (1-3" Drop) w/BLACK Polyurethane Bushings (13pc Set): Adjustable Suspension System
description: We understand that you may not be completely satisfied with the current wheel gap in your C4 Corvette. As fellow owners of two C4s, we can relate to the frustration of seeing our beloved cars sit higher than desired, especially after installing a set of attractive wheels. While some individuals attempt to address this issue by using OEM hardware to adjust the suspension, the results often fall short in terms of achieving the desired drop, material finish, and ride quality. At BDE-Systems, we specialize in developing lowering kits specifically tailored for Corvettes, and we are pleased to present our refined version of the 11" bolt kit. Short of opting for a custom coil-over/track setup, our C4 Lowering Kits offer a swift and cost-effective solution to enhance both the aesthetics and ride of your Corvette. These kits have been available for purchase on our website, BDE-Systems.com, as well as on renowned platforms such as The CorvetteForum and eBay since 2014. We are proud to announce that as of 2023, our kits are also accessible through AMAZON.com LLC. It is important to highlight that the lowering/ride height provided by our kit is fully adjustable to your preference and wheel/tire setup. The development of this C4 kit was guided by our own 1987 and 1994 Corvette C4s, as well as invaluable feedback from select members of The CorvetteForum and their respective vehicles. This collaborative effort allowed us to consider a wide range of suspension requirements and formulate the comprehensive kit we present to you today. Thank you for considering our C4 Lowering Kit. We are confident that it will not only transform the appearance of your Corvette but also significantly improve its ride quality.
